to the Play Store, if

00:26:45.210 --> 00:26:46.810
they don't have the game.

00:26:46.810 --> 00:26:50.420
And if there are more multiple
versions, we let you decide

00:26:50.420 --> 00:26:53.940
which is store entry to send
the users to with the check

00:26:53.940 --> 00:26:56.400
box on the Play console.

