00:27:21.810 --> 00:27:24.720
So it's Thanksgiving fairly
soon, I guess.

00:27:24.720 --> 00:27:27.720
And I that "Angry Fruit Fall"
game is stuck in my brain.

00:27:27.720 --> 00:27:29.690
I really want to make
that happen.

00:27:29.690 --> 00:27:31.770
And it's not quite the same
as the original game.

00:27:31.770 --> 00:27:32.940
And we're adding new content.

