00:28:18.440 --> 00:28:19.270
the original three.

00:28:19.270 --> 00:28:21.740
They won't see anything of the
new stuff you've uploaded.

00:28:21.740 --> 00:28:25.590
However, your testers
see everything.

00:28:25.590 --> 00:28:27.820
And they'll see your in-progress
graphics and mock

00:28:27.820 --> 00:28:29.060
you for it.

00:28:29.060 --> 00:28:32.700
Now, once you've hit publish,
everybody gets to see all the

00:28:32.700 --> 00:28:34.640
achievements and
all the icons.

00:28:34.640 --> 00:28:35.970
And that's everybody.

00:28:35.970 --> 00:28:40.060
So if the original "Angry
Fruit" users have the

00:28:40.060 --> 00:28:41.220
achievement UI.

