00:30:47.240 --> 00:30:49.120
And they're also not
wearing glass.

00:30:49.120 --> 00:30:51.445
JAEWOONG JUNG: Hm,
that's right.

00:30:51.445 --> 00:30:54.430
They look suspicious,
which makes me

00:30:54.430 --> 00:30:57.920
introduce the next subject--

00:30:57.920 --> 00:31:00.020
managing.

00:31:00.020 --> 00:31:03.170
"Angry Fruit Fall" went totally
viral and began to

00:31:03.170 --> 00:31:06.050
attract cheaters, as
Dan pointed out.

00:31:06.050 --> 00:31:08.830
So how should you
deal with them?

00:31:08.830 --> 00:31:11.630
Coming back to this leaderboard,
we now believe

00:31:11.630 --> 00:31:14.180
the first and the second
place are cheaters.

00:31:14.180 --> 00:31:16.910
You want to hide them
from the game.

00:31:16.910 --> 00:31:20.960
So let's build an admin
website with

00:31:20.960 --> 00:31:24.340
the hide player function.

