Most players don't know their
player IDs, because we don't

00:33:29.250 --> 00:33:31.660
have UI to show them.

00:33:31.660 --> 00:33:35.750
So it's not like she can tell
you, my player ID is this,

00:33:35.750 --> 00:33:36.230
this, this.

00:33:36.230 --> 00:33:38.190
Please give me back my scores.

00:33:38.190 --> 00:33:39.340
But don't worry.

00:33:39.340 --> 00:33:41.500
There is not only one but
two ways to figure

00:33:41.500 --> 00:33:44.610
out player's IDs.

00:33:44.610 --> 00:33:49.200
First, you provide this list
hidden players API.

00:33:49.200 --> 00:33:52.360
